<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c2">(من كنيته أَبُو الصَّلْت)</span><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>٣٩٥٧ -<span class="c5"> أَبُو الصَّلْت:</span> شُرَيْح بن عبيد<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>الْحِمصِي الْحَضْرَمِيّ.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c5">حدث عَن:</span> أبي أُمَامَة.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>كناه البُخَارِيّ.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>٣٩٥٨ -<span class="c5"> أَبُو الصَّلْت:</span> الثَّقَفِيّ.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span><span class="c5">حدث عَن:</span> عمر رَضِي الله عَنهُ.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span><span class="c5">روى عَنهُ:</span> أَبُو إِسْحَاق، وَعبد الله بن عمار<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span>الْيَمَانِيّ.<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span>قَالَه البُخَارِيّ.<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span>٣٩٥٩ - أَبُو الصَّلْت.<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span><span class="c5">حدث عَن:</span> أبي هُرَيْرَة.<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span><span class="c5">روى عَنهُ:</span> عَليّ بن زيد بن جدعَان.<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span>٣٩٦٠ -<span class="c5"> أَبُو الصَّلْت:</span> جد عِيسَى بن معمر.<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span><span class="c5">حدث عَن:</span> كَعْب الْأَحْبَار.<a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p16"></span><span class="c5">روى عَنهُ:</span> صَفْوَان بن عَمْرو الْحِمصِي.<a href="#p16" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p17"></span>٣٩٦١ -<span class="c5"> أَبُو الصَّلْت:</span> الْبَصْرِيّ.<a href="#p17" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p18"></span><span class="c5">حدث عَن:</span> أنس بن مَالك.<a href="#p18" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p19"></span><span class="c5">روى عَنهُ:</span> سَلام بن مِسْكين.<a href="#p19" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p20"></span>٣٩٦٢ -<span class="c5"> أَبُو الصَّلْت:</span> بياع الزَّاد، كُوفِي.<a href="#p20" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p21"></span><span class="c5">حدث عَن:</span> أبي عقرب.<a href="#p21" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p22"></span><span class="c5">روى عَنهُ:</span> أَبُو يَعْفُور.<a href="#p22" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p23"></span>قَالَه البُخَارِيّ.<a href="#p23" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p24"></span>٣٩٦٣ -<span class="c5"> أَبُو الصَّلْت:</span> شهَاب بن خرَاش بن<a href="#p24" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p25"></span>حَوْشَب الوَاسِطِيّ.<a href="#p25" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p26"></span>نزل الشَّام،<span class="c5"> حدث عَن:</span> عبد الْملك بن عُمَيْر.<a href="#p26" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p27"></span><span class="c5">روى عَنهُ:</span> عبد الله بن مَيْمُون القداح.<a href="#p27" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p28"></span>كناه سَلمَة بن كهيل.<a href="#p28" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p29"></span>٣٩٦٤ -<span class="c5"> أَبُو الصَّلْت:</span> زَائِدَة بن قدامَة الثَّقَفِيّ<a href="#p29" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p30"></span>الْكُوفِي.<a href="#p30" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p31"></span><span class="c5">حدث عَن:</span> سُلَيْمَان الْأَعْمَش، وَمَنْصُور بن<a href="#p31" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p32"></span>الْمُعْتَمِر، وَعبد الْملك بن عُمَيْر.<a href="#p32" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p33"></span>كناه الْحُسَيْن بن عَليّ الْجعْفِيّ.<a href="#p33" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p34"></span>٣٩٦٥ -<span class="c5"> أَبُو الصَّلْت:</span> حجاج بن أبي عُثْمَان<a href="#p34" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p35"></span>الصَّواف.<a href="#p35" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p36"></span><span class="c5">حدث عَن:</span> يحيى بن أبي كثير.<a href="#p36" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p37"></span>سَمِعت مُحَمَّد بن يَعْقُوب،<span class="c5"> يَقُول:</span> سَمِعت<a href="#p37" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p38"></span>عباسا،<span class="c5"> يَقُول:</span> سَمِعت يحيى بن معِين،<a href="#p38" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p39"></span><span class="c5">يَقُول:</span> حجاج بن أبي عُثْمَان أَبُو الصَّلْت.<a href="#p39" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p40"></span>٣٩٦٦ -<span class="c5"> أَبُو الصَّلْت:</span> عبد السَّلَام بن صَالح<a href="#p40" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p41"></span>الْهَرَوِيّ.<a href="#p41" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p42"></span><span class="c5">حدث عَن:</span> عَليّ بن مُوسَى الرِّضَا.<a href="#p42" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>